values:
So yeahhh. Pretty much all ive been doing is hitting the mall and the movies all the time with Tim. Yesterday i went to his house and we chilled there, then we went to the mall. I saw everyone. Bethani >.<, Zack >.<, Joeii, Rachel, Erin, Eddie, Sara, Puggy, Nicole, and a bunch of other people i used to hang out there with last summer. I even saw Dirk. He looked upset so i talked to him and him and his girl were having problems. I saw him in the same spot we used to hang out at and the same spot where i broke his heart. *sigh* it killed me. Then me and Tim got in the elevator which made it even WORSE cuz thats where me and Dirk always went. I almost cried. It took all i had to hold back tears. So then Me, Tim, and Danny went to the movies and saw Clerks 2. While we were waiting on Danny we talked and i watched Tim skate until it startd raining and we talked about how we were going to sneak some people in. Which i never helped lol but i was suppossed to but they kinda took over. But all in all the movie was good until Tim got mad at me, which really fkn' sucked but everything was better eventually. I love that kid sooo much. Then we came home and talked on the phone about a buncha stuff. I ended up bawling my eyes out for some stupid stuff, but then i wrote him a long ass note and went to be and when i woke up everything was alot better amazingly. I was suppossed to hang out with Tim today but i ended up being forced to the fair which i was kinda glad to go. Its mine and kevins tradition, and he always gets me roses. Well i wanted to ride rides. I didnt care how big or scary, cuz i dont like most of them. But we went on some really cool ones including the Drop Zone which is fuckin' scary but awesome lol i didnt even scream and i made through it!! I was proud. I got a teddy and a rose of course. I saw like a bazzillion people i knew and people i aint seen in forever. Like Travis, Danny, Danny, Dylan, Sam, and a bunch of others. So yeah. Now im home and it sucks cuz' Tim aint callin' me adn i wanted to sneak out and see him. *sigh* hes probably mad that i didnt hang with him today but i know ill make up for it i promise i will but he wont ever read this so its not like he'll know. But ive been tryin to get ahold of him forever. 
But yeah 2mrrw im most deff. hanging with him so NOONE try and change my plans. Then Wednesday im going to see Clerks 2 again cuz' it was just that damn good, then Friday and Saturday i have to go back to the fair for the Demolition Derby. Its 3 bucks to get in. Then afterwards im going to go ride some more rides and shit and its gonna be freakin' awesome. I really hope Tim goes with me though. Im really falling for that kid hard and idk what to do..It hasnt even been that long. But idk imma go wait on him to NOT call me i guess. 
//Peace/\Love\\

So the lockin was pretty fun. I hung out with Emily and Sara for the longest time just chillin' and messin' with people and dancin' and stuff. It was pretty freakin' hilarious. Lol So then i hung out with Eddie the other bit of the time.... We talked and messed around and stuff. Uhhmm...I hung out with Aj, Brandon, Billy, Joeii, and some other guys. We played DDR for like EVER and a freakin' day. Lol i whooped their asses. Hellz yes. And they got beat by a girl. I felt pretty damn cool. :D Then Joeii FINALLY got me to go on the go karts with him. >.< Gahh. It actually wasnt that bad Lol. I had an "oh shit bad" lmao. You just had to be there. So then i hung out with Joeii and Billy and all the rest of them. It was fun. I mean, we pretty much just chilled. There was like NO drama other than me and Emily messin' with Codey and people but other than that it was pretty damn cool. lol 
Then ever since saturday ive been hanging out with Tim Gentry a HELL of alot. :D its been pretty awesome. Yuppp. :D Need i say more? Yeah. Wellllll.....Theres not more to say but im out of here so leave my comments. Kthnx? 
&hearts;
